ng-container(*ngIf="loaded")
    div(class="min-h-full px-6 py-4", *ngIf="MENU == 'info'")
        wiz-portal-works-project-info

    ng-container(*ngIf="project.accessLevel(['admin', 'manager', 'user', 'guest'])")
        div(class="min-h-full px-6 py-4", *ngIf="MENU == 'member'")
            wiz-portal-works-project-member
        ng-container(*ngIf="MENU == 'issueboard'")
            wiz-portal-works-project-issueboard
        ng-container(*ngIf="MENU == 'meeting'")
            wiz-portal-works-project-meeting
        ng-container(*ngIf="MENU == 'drive'")
            wiz-portal-works-project-drive
        div(class="min-h-full px-6 py-4", *ngIf="MENU == 'wiki'")
            wiz-portal-works-project-wiki

    ng-container(*ngIf="project.accessLevel(['visitor'])")
        div(class="p-8", *ngIf="MENU != 'info'")
            div(class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 py-16 text-center")
                div(class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center")
                    i(class="ti ti-lock text-5xl text-neutral-300 mb-4")
                    p(class="text-base font-medium text-neutral-700") 접근 권한이 없습니다
                    p(class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-400") 아래 참가하기 버튼을 눌러 프로젝트에 참가해주세요
                    button(class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 mt-6 bg-blue-500 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors", (click)="joinProject()")
                        i(class="ti ti-user-plus text-base")
                        | 참가하기
